697
00:38:19,740 --> 00:38:21,259
and the imperial great grandson
is found,

698
00:38:22,499 --> 00:38:23,940
we'll leave Xichang

699
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:27,660
and live freely in Laolan Pass.

700
00:38:27,820 --> 00:38:28,899
