728
00:41:18,979 --> 00:41:20,378
I can see you're particularly concerned

729
00:41:20,379 --> 00:41:21,418
about this matter.

730
00:41:21,419 --> 00:41:22,420
Of course.

731
00:41:22,499 --> 00:41:23,819
The first time I met you two,

732
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:25,139
