733
00:41:25,140 --> 00:41:26,460
It made me uncomfortable.

734
00:41:27,100 --> 00:41:28,779
Why do you still want to ask?

735
00:41:30,620 --> 00:41:32,020
Young Master

736
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:35,779
