776
00:43:01,140 --> 00:43:02,418
I can no longer hide

777
00:43:02,419 --> 00:43:03,859
the feminine side of me.

778
00:43:04,059 --> 00:43:06,058
So, Father let Liu Chengfeng

779
00:43:06,059 --> 00:43:07,739
