835
00:45:29,419 --> 00:45:30,299
Really?

836
00:45:31,660 --> 00:45:32,938
Then I'll sing it seriously this time.

837
00:45:32,939 --> 00:45:33,739
All right.

838
00:45:34,660 --> 00:45:36,580
I'll stand up and sing seriously now.

